<main>
    <h3 class = "hh3">Short Biography</h3>
        <img src="me.jpg" style="float: right;">
    <p class="text">Zayd was born is the USA and came to Australia 5 months later. He loves books and aviation, so when he got into authoring books, he combined those two to make novels both fictional and real that entertain as well as inform. His books are mainly targeted at teens and adults due to the difficult vocabulary and consistent theme of danger and eventually a new hope in an unimaginable way. His books are now easier than ever to read as he has now published them online. To read more about his incredible feats as a writer and more info about borrowing his books, go to the About section or click <a href = "#">here</a>.</p>
