    <h3 class= 'hh3'>Latest book</h3>
    
<br>
    <img src="Front.jpg" id ="image">
    <h3 class="hh3">First Paragraph</h3>
<p class="text">
    <br>
    This book is not for the feint-hearted nor is it for the people who love Disney movies. This book will make you want to chatter in fear. I mean how bad could it really be….
    <br>
    <br>
“This is the FAA in partnership with the FBI; we order you to land immediately!” John is getting his type-rating for Cessna 172, and Dave is the flight instructor, and this is not how they had expected their routine training flight to go. For the uninitiated people who live on Mars, a type-rating is like a license to be allowed to fly a specific aircraft. Anyways, this sudden command shocked both of them and John, the pilot flying accidently put the plane in a nosedive. Dave, the pilot monitoring had to pull up and level off. “We should probably respond to the FAA now,” said John. “This is Charlie Echo Bravo 93, we would like to ask…umm… the reason for this command please,” asked Dave. “Charlie Echo Bravo 93, you have broken the law and thus will be arrested once you land,” replied the FAA agent from the fighter jet that intercepted them. Oh boy…..
</p>
